跟for 一样<br />
while 也是循环结构的一种<br />
但是他只是检测condition 是否为true<br />
<a href="http://lh6.ggpht.com/-m0YxP5CUc2w/UoyAQAIhNfI/AAAAAAAAGLc/KblDRq4LKNE/s1600-h/image2.png"><img alt="image" border="0" height="88" src="http://lh3.ggpht.com/-jigLIKwT4pQ/UoyAQ4lb0BI/AAAAAAAAGLk/rFfM_aTStpw/image_thumb.png?imgmax=800" style="border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; display: inline;" title="image" width="191" /></a> <br />
<blockquote>
condition<br />
每当while 运行code body之前，它为检查condition是否为true，true 时执行，false则不执行</blockquote>
比如说这个for 语句：<br />
<a href="http://lh4.ggpht.com/-CYBUzpKzu60/UoyARWTCvEI/AAAAAAAAGLs/rS6q3-isqG8/s1600-h/image%25255B3%25255D.png"><img alt="image" border="0" height="118" src="http://lh5.ggpht.com/-nLmtgtOrLNM/UoyASPZAVPI/AAAAAAAAGLw/YjgaVUNXTGI/image_thumb%25255B1%25255D.png?imgmax=800" style="border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; display: inline;" title="image" width="401" /></a> <br />
运行结果：<br />
<a href="http://lh4.ggpht.com/-Hk6WYrG39Uw/UoyAStcZ-bI/AAAAAAAAGL4/xojP3NGK2zI/s1600-h/image%25255B6%25255D.png"><img alt="image" border="0" height="300" src="http://lh6.ggpht.com/-PtELdZR2iOA/UoyATVlMlgI/AAAAAAAAGMA/mK6QZcV4Abk/image_thumb%25255B2%25255D.png?imgmax=800" style="border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; display: inline;" title="image" width="300" /></a> <br />
转换成while 语句的话：<br />
<a href="http://lh3.ggpht.com/-Ao4IdT2k7os/UoyAT0uTRoI/AAAAAAAAGMI/LvaTj1YK8dE/s1600-h/image%25255B18%25255D.png"><img alt="image" border="0" height="163" src="http://lh6.ggpht.com/-nOQ9XyNVNYk/UoyAUcuwwwI/AAAAAAAAGMQ/q8GhwZ4pGQg/image_thumb%25255B6%25255D.png?imgmax=800" style="border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; display: inline;" title="image" width="399" /></a> <br />
输出结果是一样的：<br />
<a href="http://lh5.ggpht.com/-lIOvmoqwTf0/UoyAU0OB4kI/AAAAAAAAGMc/uXk0CXsRgwE/s1600-h/image%25255B21%25255D.png"><img alt="image" border="0" height="300" src="http://lh5.ggpht.com/-GlLGN-N3r54/UoyAVhxGkhI/AAAAAAAAGMk/fK9EMuEEJ-4/image_thumb%25255B7%25255D.png?imgmax=800" style="border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; display: inline;" title="image" width="300" /></a> <br />
整个代码基本上就是：<br />
<blockquote>
检查i是不是小于0<br />
如果是的话，运行代码，i++会让i增加1<br />
如果不是的话，退出整个while循环</blockquote>
