注意：记得break！不然while 会疯狂的！</blockquote>
输出结果：<br />
<a href="http://lh4.ggpht.com/-WD3AFyMkSIE/UoyAXlt9zWI/AAAAAAAAGM8/ZIGDCTFq5oY/s1600-h/image%25255B27%25255D.png"><img alt="image" border="0" height="300" src="http://lh4.ggpht.com/-RkC6w45y4ak/UoyAYMczd_I/AAAAAAAAGNE/U_n490d9SqA/image_thumb%25255B9%25255D.png?imgmax=800" style="border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; display: inline;" title="image" width="300" /></a> <br />
while (true)<br />
代表condition 一直都为true<br />
所以while 循环一直（都很疯狂的）运行着<br />
当i大于9的时候<br />
break语句就会（很理性的）告诉while：<br />
<blockquote>
喂！你该休息了！</blockquote>
于是while 就休息了…<br />
